title: Tomb of Hakaz-Ghesh
story: For many years the tomb of Hakaz-Ghesh was considered lost. These days it is badly infested by cats, which don't care about the past of the place. It is rumored that the tomb is rich with treasures of gold and jewels and ancient books.

notes.text: A mouth-shaped door with two keyholes to the west.
A dying gnome, an exotic spear, a crowbar and a shield among his belongings.
A stuffed halfling with a golden key in their hands.
A witch, resting on the ground.
A golden key hidden in a crack of the floor.
